Subject: [PATCH] Add Innovation Engine - Automatic fallback and verification

This patch adds systematic innovation capabilities to OpenClaw:
- Intercept all tool calls
- Auto-fallback on failure
- Mandatory verification
- Pattern learning

---
 openclaw/src/core/tool-execution.ts          |  45 ++++
 openclaw/src/innovation/engine.ts            | 245 ++++++++++++++++++
 openclaw/src/innovation/verifiers.ts         | 120 +++++++++
 openclaw/src/innovation/learner.ts           | 178 +++++++++++++
 openclaw/src/innovation/index.ts             |  15 ++
 openclaw/src/config/innovation.yaml          |  82 ++++++
